# Textures Directory

Place PBR texture sets here:
- albedo.jpg (or baseColor)
- normal.jpg
- roughness.jpg
- metallic.jpg
- ao.jpg (ambient occlusion)
- height.jpg (displacement)

Recommended formats:
- WebP for mobile (smaller size)
- KTX2 with BasisU for GPU compression
- ASTC for iOS, ETC2 for Android
